name: Turtles Island
description:
It looked like an island. As he started his living life, he did not realize that there was another living underneath. This creature, which did not care about the life that lived on it, allowed them to live. He was too old to move on. Everyone who wondered and loved him had left this land before him.

If he were gone, would life continue on him? Those who loved him perhaps felt that he should come to them now.
